OL,3,CTributes to 'extraordinary'
OL,4,CHillsborough campaigner who lost 18-
OL,5,Cyear-old son
OL,7,FTributes have been paid to an
OL,8,F"extraordinary man" who was a "pillar"
OL,9,Fof the Hillsborough justice movement
OL,10,Fafter his son was killed in the
OL,11,Ftragedy.
OL,13,FBarry Devonside became a crucial
OL,14,Ffigure in the campaign after his son
OL,15,FChristopher, 18, died in the 1989 FA
OL,16,FCup semi-final that killed 97
OL,17,FLiverpool fans.
OL,19,FHe died earlier in August and was laid
OL,20,Fto rest in Formby on 13 August.
