OL,7,FFriend and fellow campaigner Steve
OL,8,FKelly, whose brother was also killed
OL,9,Fat Hillsborough, said he was an
OL,10,F"extraordinary man" who he was "proud
OL,11,Fto campaign alongside."
OL,13,FSteve said: "Barry was such a
OL,14,Ftenacious man. He attended every day
OL,15,Fof every inquest, every trial - even
OL,16,Fon the days we didn't need to be
OL,17,Fthere, he was there and we all learnt
OL,18,Fa lot from him - he was fantastic.
OL,26,@rD@AOUrD@SO]rD@`OUsD@WO]uD@MOU
