OL,3,CTributes to 'extraordinary'
OL,4,CHillsborough campaigner who lost 18-
OL,5,Cyear-old son
OL,7,F"Barry led the charge. If you needed
OL,8,Fto go into the trenches, he was the
OL,9,Fperson you wanted by your side and I
OL,10,Fwas very proud to be alongside him in
OL,11,Fthe campaign."
OL,13,FCharlotte Hennessy, whose dad James
OL,14,Fwas killed, also paid a tribute.
OL,16,FShe said: "He was one of the backbones
OL,17,Fof the fight, a pillar of the campaign
OL,18,F- I have never known someone who could
OL,19,Freel off so many dates, times,
OL,20,Freferences - he had the memory of an
OL,21,Felephant.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G4/7
