OL,3,CTributes to 'extraordinary'
OL,4,CHillsborough campaigner who lost 18-
OL,5,Cyear-old son
OL,7,F"He was so organised and had so many
OL,8,Ffiles in relation to Hillsborough.
OL,10,F"He was very, very determined in the
OL,11,Ffight for truth and justice. He was a
OL,12,Freally big character."
OL,14,FIn 2019, at the retrial of
OL,15,FHillsborough match commander David
OL,16,FDuckinfield, Barry explained how he
OL,17,Fhad travelled to the 1989 FA Cup semi-
OL,18,Ffinal with his son, but they were sat
OL,19,Fin different parts of Hillsborough
OL,20,FStadium.
OL,26,@oD@AOUtD@VO]
