OL,4,CHillsborough campaigner who lost 18-
OL,5,Cyear-old son
OL,7,FHe could only watch on as the tragedy
OL,8,Ftook place.
OL,10,FBarry visited two hospitals and a
OL,11,Fboys' club before having to identify
OL,12,FChristopher's body in the stadium's
OL,13,Fgym.
OL,15,FNicola Brook, legal director at
OL,16,FBroudie Jackson Canter, posted on X on
OL,17,F13 August: "Today we said our final
OL,18,Fgoodbyes to this absolute legend.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G6/7
